Package: naptanr
Title: Call the Naptan API Through R
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
    person("Tom", "Westlake", , "tom.westlake@dft.gov.uk", role = c("aut")),
    person("Francesca", "Bryden", , "francesca.bryden@dft.gov.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Sara", "Smith", , "sara.smith@dft.gov.uk", role = c("aut")))
Description: The NaptanR package makes it easy to call the National Public Transport Access Nodes (Naptan) API (<https://naptan.api.dft.gov.uk/swagger/index.html>). This allows users to download Naptan transport information, for the full dataset, by ATCO code, or by name of region.  
